nodes.text: An octopedal sentient species hailed from the planet Yoberra, in the Outer Rim's Airam sector. Jomo, a member of the species, won the octoped division of the Mobquet Presents: Fastest Land Beings race of 22 BBY.

The species was mentioned in "New Galaxy's Fastest Hexaped," an article published as part of HoloNet News Vol. 531 52, a simulation of an in-universe news source that led up to the release of Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones. This particular article was published on April 18, 2002.
